# Propie Project Rules

This is a real estate marketplace platform.

Tech Stack:
- Next.js
- TypeScript
- GraphQL
- Supabase
- PostgreSQL
- Tailwind
- Playwright

Architecture:
- Owner
- Agent
- Client

Rules:
- Use TypeScript strictly.
- Avoid any.
- Prefer server components.
- Follow existing GraphQL patterns.
- Create Playwright tests for new features.
- Keep UI responsive.